{"tid":1768770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(向連登仔宣戰）港示威持續　王毅敦促外交官員表現「鬥爭精神」　多名外交官開 Twitter","createTime":"2019-12-04T10:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T11:40:01.000Z","uid":50457,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"12e9d967237a68394e1b36591f6024e98b1edbd6","tid":1768770,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:08:10.000Z","msg":"反送中運動以來，不少示威者和政團希望透過「國際戰線」爭取外國支持，另一邊廂北京亦嘗試加強國際輿論影響力。路透社引述消息指，在香港反送中運動及中美貿易戰持續之際，國務委員兼外交部長王毅在上月發出指示，要求一眾外交官員表現出更強的「鬥爭精神」（fighting spirit），積極宣傳北京的觀點。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述三名知情人士透露，國務委員兼外交部長王毅上月在一次外交部的慶祝活動上，敦促官員面對國際挑戰時，要表現出更強的「鬥爭精神」（fighting spirit）。<br />\n雖然他在會上並沒有作出明確的指示，但會後隨即有多名高級外交官員開設 Twitter 帳戶，部分已開始用來反擊批評北京的輿論。此外，本周開始中國外交部亦開設了 Twitter。<br />\n報道指，當日有過千名現任及前官員在北京出席會議，活動同時是為了慶祝外交部成立70週年。其中一名有份出席活動的消息人士形容，這是他們首次被要求表現更多「鬥爭精神」。<br />\n報道指，在過去數月內有最少十多名中國大使及外交官員設立 Twitter 帳戶，包括中國駐奧地利、伊朗、馬爾代夫、沙地阿拉伯、南非、美國及英國的大使。而 Twitter 則表明，政府的官方聲音是構成該社交平台的重要元素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E6%95%A6%E4%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E7%258E%258B%25E6%25AF%2585%25E6%2595%25A6%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=cb477d34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%2580%258F%25E7%25A4%25BE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C-%25E7%258E%258B%25E6%25AF%2585%25E6%2595%25A6%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%258F%25BE-%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%2F&h=b9372881\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE-%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E6%95%A6%E4%BF%83%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE-%E9%AC%A5%E7%88%AD%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E/</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 戰線要面對國家級挑戰，所有連登冷氣軍準備應戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce278d2f83fa24645ddbf7d3eab76c335b36e70","tid":1768770,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"(感謝list on Twitter!) 通過Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7f3770f574146398ac4e99e14e05fff84a1120bb","tid":1768770,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"對唔住，借個位宣傳一下，特首選委過半有望。<br />\n<br />\n特首選委戰線 &mdash; 七個同行手足，成立工會，重光勞工界！只剩唔夠四個月時間！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768465\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768465</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"364f3cb3f353cdf78be920c939988af1d237927c","tid":1768770,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"連登仔，快開account<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d33144bd4f04671bde07d787c431024107e0501","tid":1768770,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T10:11